+----------------+
|Game Description|
+----------------+

Conquer the Big Apple with hidden objects and mini-games! After leaving her small hometown with just big dreams and a journalism degree, Laura needs your help to navigate her unpredicatable career and love life in NYC!

+----------------------------------+
|Instructions / System Requirements|
+----------------------------------+

No install or crack is required for this portable version. Extract the ZIP file and create a shortcut to the executable (EXE) to play.

- Windows XP/ Vista / 7

- 1 GHz processor speed

- 128 MB RAM

- 512 MB VRAM 16 or 32-bit Video Card

- 16 bit DirectX compatible sound card

- DirectX 8.1

